FBIS3-23154 "jptot010__l94117" JPRS-TOT-94-010-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 10 March 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA LEBANON Bomb in Zuq Musbih Church Kills 10, Injures 40 `Big Explosion' In Church, Casualties NC2702080194 (Clandestine) Radio Free Lebanon in Arabic 0747 GMT 27 Feb 94 NC2702080194 (Clandestine) Radio Free Lebanon Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [See SELECTED VIDEO REPORTS in the front of this Terrorism Report for TV coverage of this incident] [Excerpt] A horrendous crime with the proportions of a massacre was committed in the Church of Sayyidat al-Najat in Wata Zuq Mich'il a short while ago. A big explosion occurred in the church while worshippers were taking part in a mass. Initial information indicates that a large number of people were killed or injured. Casualties are being taken to the hospitals in the area, particularly the Sayyidat Lubnan Hospital, which is crowded with casualties. [passage omitted]
